                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The "advantages" of chanter pulling are that the group loses almost no dps for the puller, monks, SK, warriors, even bards all do considerably more DPS than you(personally..pets are free dmg <img src="images/smiles/icon_razz.gif" alt="icon_razz.gif" border="0" />) will unless all out nukeing. once you get a good rythm down, you can have a Mob -with whatever debuffs you need to do- waiting for yer party to kill just when the last one dies, so its continuous killing, no wasted time. I change up how i pull, and sometimes its just faster to send pet or tank into room and mez adds than it is to actually pull... but i still take control of this anyway.  If your party is killing a mob in 30 secs or less, paci pulling probably isn't necessary.
<br />

<br />
a quick note about ldon, GET MAPS, and lead your group. so much easier to do your job when you have an idea of whats comeing and you have a goal to reach. instead of just stumbling blindly behind whichever monk or warrior feels like being the boss today.
<br />

<br />
D</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
