                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I have been pulling since i was a little chanter in OT. Everyone said the things i would, we aren't DPS so it's no big loss to the gruop, not to mention pre pop mezzes last a good bit and you can stack up the mobs for the group to kill which means faster exp. 
<br />

<br />
I do alot of pulling at 65 in LDON because i can paci the mobs, and would only decline the chance to pull to a bard (who if you get the right one are killer pullers) 
<br />

<br />
Convincing a group to let you pull shouldn't be terribly difficult for if they are wise, they know how great chanters are and besides, if someone over pulls we are gonna die anyways so it's not like it's a bad thing <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Dionysia
