                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Proximity and damage allow the warrior to get mobs on them while you're out pulling.  4 taunts to pull a mob off was in regards to no damage being done.  Because you do no damage on a pull, your Bonus Hate isn't as high as it could be.  However, if you nuked when you pulled, you'd cause headaches for a warrior MT, heh.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
