                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am preferred puller for guild groups.
<br />

<br />
3 spells you should keep up:
<br />

<br />
1. Pacification
<br />
2. Boggle
<br />
3. Bind sight
<br />

<br />
well, and mez of course.  Always pull with boggle unless you are low and mana or have a good MT that can grab aggro quickly. 
<br />

<br />
Bind sight is probably one of the most under utilized spells we have for pulling.  Enchanters can basically see everywhere with a quick cast of a spell.  If you are lucky you can also used bind sight to "see" your way through a zone to check on mobs, etc.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=450192" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.shadesofthevoid.com/images/sig/ed.jpg" border="0" /></a>
<br />
<span style="color: darkblue"><span style="font-weight: bold">High Elven Coercer</span></span> 
<br />
<a href="http://www.shadesofthevoid.com" target="_blank" class="postlink"><span style="color: darkblue"><span style="font-weight: bold">Shades of the Void</span></span> </a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
