                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Pretty much everything has been said here, some things I agree with more that others but its very dependant on your own personal style which I firmly believe there is no wrong style.
<br />

<br />
However I just wanted to point out that pulling for your group and keeping a charmed pet doesnt have to be mutually exclusive.  We can potentially be the highest DPS class in EQ with a hasted charmed pet so it would be a shame not to capitalize on it.  The beauty of it all, is that while you are poking around for your next victim, scrappy is still having a field day with the mob back in the main camp <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=4714" target="_blank" class="postlink">Khayne</a> 
